comments: Quickley (NYK) moves his hands forward towards LeVert (IND) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.

After making initial contact with the ball, Quickley (NYK) slides his hand off of the ball and he moves forward into LeVert (IND) while he is airborne, delivering contact that affects his shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) is already in Holiday's (IND) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Sabonis (IND) places a stayed hand to Rose's (NYK) hip and marginal contact occurs as Rose passes the ball.
Sabonis (IND) applies a rested forearm to Randle's (NYK) side and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Turner (IND) applies his left hand to Randle's (NYK) front and absorbs the marginal contact as he defends the shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) is already in Barrett's (NYK) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Sabonis (IND) ends his dribble and hops consecutively on the same foot after his gather.
Barrett (NYK) brushes Sabonis' (IND) off arm as he defends the shot near the rim, and contact is marginal.
Rose (NYK) makes contact with Sabonis' (IND) arm as he defends the put back attempt.
Randle (NYK) is already in Holiday's (IND) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Sabonis (IND) applies his hand to Rose's (NYK) off arm and immediately removes his hand as Rose begins his upward shooting motion.
Brogdon (IND) and Rose (NYK) come together at the same spot and incidental contact occurs as they attempt to secure the rebound.
Brogdon (IND) steps on the baseline after he secures possession.
Sabonis (IND) and Gibson (NYK) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Randle (NYK) briefly grasps Turner's (IND) jersey and marginal contact occurs during rebounding.
Sabonis (IND) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Rose (NYK) legally contests LeVert's (IND) jump shot attempt.
